parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Spark Plug Blow Out due to Stripped Cylinder Head Threads
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the spark plug can cause engine misfires, decreased engine performance, and potentially lead to engine damage, which can result in costly repairs and compromise vehicle safety.

engine misfires
decreased engine performance
engine stalling
difficulty starting the engine
loud engine noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Unintended Activation of Anti-Lock Braking System (ABS)
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended activation of the ABS can cause the vehicle to lose traction, making it difficult to control, which can lead to accidents or near-miss situations.
symptoms: The brake system warning light illuminates on the dashboard

the vehicle's brakes pulse or vibrate
the vehicle's wheels lock up or skid
the vehicle's speed is reduced unexpectedly.
